This [[Special:MyLanguage/Template:Noticebox|noticebox]] can be added to pages to mark them for deletion by [[Special:MyLanguage/VRCWiki:Wiki Moderators|Wiki Moderators]]. Pages with this template are added to the category [[Special:MyLanguage/:Category:Pages Marked for Deletion|Pages Marked for Deletion]]. Adding <code><nowiki>~~~~</nowiki></code> to the second parameter signs the template with your name.

== Pre-made reasons ==
When possible, prefer to use a pre-made reason, which are automatically translated & localized.

=== Empty or missing content ===
 <nowiki>{{Delete/Empty|~~~~}}</nowiki>
{{Delete/Empty}}

== Custom reason ==
 <nowiki>{{Delete|A detailed and descriptive reason.|~~~~}}</nowiki>
{{Delete|A detailed and descriptive reason.}}

'''Note:''' If you need to transclude this template without adding the page to this category, use the parameter <code>nocat=1</code>.
